<span class="n">n</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">100</span>
<span class="n">há»c_phÃ­</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">random</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">normal</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1000</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">300</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">n</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">mÃ¡y_tÃ­nh_báº£ng</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">random</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">binomial</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">expit</span><span class="p">((</span><span class="n">há»c_phÃ­</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">há»c_phÃ­</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">())</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">há»c_phÃ­</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">std</span><span class="p">())).</span><span class="n">astype</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">bool</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">Ä‘iá»ƒm_enem</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">random</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">normal</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">200</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">50</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">mÃ¡y_tÃ­nh_báº£ng</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">0.7</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">há»c_phÃ­</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">200</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">Ä‘iá»ƒm_enem</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Ä‘iá»ƒm_enem</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">Ä‘iá»ƒm_enem</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">min</span><span class="p">())</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">Ä‘iá»ƒm_enem</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">max</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="n">Ä‘iá»ƒm_enem</span> <span class="o">*=</span> <span class="mi">1000</span>

<span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">dict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Ä‘iá»ƒm_enem</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">Ä‘iá»ƒm_enem</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">há»c_phÃ­</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">há»c_phÃ­</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">mÃ¡y_tÃ­nh_báº£ng</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">mÃ¡y_tÃ­nh_báº£ng</span><span class="p">))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">plt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">figure</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">figsize</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="n">sns</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">boxplot</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">y</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"Ä‘iá»ƒm_enem"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"mÃ¡y_tÃ­nh_báº£ng"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">data</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="n">set_title</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">' Äiá»ƒm ENEM theo viá»‡c trang bá»‹ MÃ¡y tÃ­nh báº£ng trong Lá»›p há»c'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">plt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">show</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="output_3_0.png" alt="png" /></p>

<p>Äá»ƒ hiá»ƒu hÆ¡n váº¥n Ä‘á» Ä‘Æ¡n giáº£n nÃ y, hÃ£y cÃ¹ng báº¯t Ä‘áº§u vá»›i viá»‡c thiáº¿t láº­p má»™t sá»‘ kÃ­ hiá»‡u. ÄÃ¢y lÃ  ngÃ´n ngá»¯ chung Ä‘á»ƒ nÃ³i vá» 
 quan há»‡ nhÃ¢n quáº£. Gá»i \(T_i\) lÃ  lÆ°á»£ng can thiá»‡p Ä‘á»‘i vá»›i cÃ¡ nhÃ¢n i.</p>

<p>$
T_i=\begin{cases}
1 \ \text{náº¿u cÃ¡ thá»ƒ i tiáº¿p nháº­n can thiá»‡p}<br />
0 \ \text{náº¿u ngÆ°á»£c láº¡i}<br />
\end{cases}
$</p>

<p>Can thiá»‡p  á»Ÿ Ä‘Ã¢y khÃ´ng nháº¥t thiáº¿t lÃ  Ä‘iá»u trá»‹ y táº¿ hoáº·c báº¥t cá»© thá»© gÃ¬ liÃªn quan Ä‘áº¿n lÄ©nh vá»±c y táº¿. Thay vÃ o Ä‘Ã³, nÃ³ chá»‰ lÃ  má»™t thuáº­t ngá»¯ chÃºng ta dÃ¹ng Ä‘á»ƒ nÃ³i vá» má»™t biá»‡n phÃ¡p/hÃ nh Ä‘á»™ng/chÆ°Æ¡ng trÃ¬nh/sÃ¡ng kiáº¿n mÃ  chÃºng ta muá»‘n tÃ¬m hiá»ƒu tÃ­nh hiá»‡u quáº£ cá»§a nÃ³. Trong trÆ°á»ng há»£p nÃ y, can thiá»‡p lÃ  viá»‡c phÃ¡t mÃ¡y tÃ­nh báº£ng cho há»c sinh.</p>

<p>Gá»i biáº¿n \(Y_i\) lÃ  káº¿t quáº£ quan sÃ¡t cho cÃ¡ thá»ƒ i.</p>

<p>$
Y_i
$</p>

<p>Káº¿t quáº£ lÃ  biáº¿n sá»‘ chÃºng ta quan tÃ¢m. ChÃºng ta muá»‘n biáº¿t liá»‡u can thiá»‡p cÃ³ áº£nh hÆ°á»Ÿng Ä‘áº¿n káº¿t quáº£ hay khÃ´ng.</p>

<p>ÄÃ¢y lÃ  Ä‘iá»u thÃº vá»‹. <strong>ThÃ¡ch thá»©c cÆ¡ báº£n cá»§a suy luáº­n nhÃ¢n quáº£</strong> lÃ  chÃºng ta khÃ´ng bao giá» cÃ³ thá»ƒ quan sÃ¡t cÃ¹ng má»™t cÃ¡ thá»ƒ Ä‘á»“ng thá»i tiáº¿p nháº­n hoáº·c khÃ´ng tiáº¿p nháº­n can thiá»‡p. Giá»‘ng nhÆ° viá»‡c chÃºng ta Ä‘i Ä‘áº¿n ngÃ£ ráº½ vÃ  chá»‰ cÃ³ thá»ƒ biáº¿t Ä‘iá»u gÃ¬ chá» Ä‘Ã³n phÃ­a trÆ°á»›c náº¿u chÃºng ta chá»n Ä‘i má»™t trong 2 con Ä‘Æ°á»ng. HÃ£y nghÄ© vá» thÆ¡ cá»§a Robert Frost <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/thorobertfrost/">[Con Ä‘Æ°á»ng chÆ°a Ä‘i/The road not taken]</a></p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Con Ä‘Æ°á»ng chia hai ngáº£ giá»¯a rá»«ng thu
NhÆ°ng than Ã´i, Ä‘Ã nh pháº£i theo má»™t lá»‘i
TÃ´i lÃ m káº» lá»¯ hÃ nh phÃ¢n vÃ¢n mÃ£i
ÄÆ°a máº¯t nhÃ¬n xuá»‘ng lá»‘i cháº¡y vá» xa
Tá»›i khÃºc cong khuáº¥t sau lÃ¹m cÃ¢y bá»¥i.
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>TÃ³m láº¡i, chÃºng ta sáº½ nÃ³i ráº¥t nhiá»u vá» cÃ¡c <strong>káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng</strong>. ChÃºng tiá»m nÄƒng vÃ¬ chÆ°a thá»±c sá»± diá»…n ra. Thay vÃ o Ä‘Ã³, chÃºng cho ta biáº¿t Ä‘iá»u gÃ¬ cÃ³ thá»ƒ xáº£y Ä‘áº¿n náº¿u cÃ³ can thiá»‡p. ÄÃ´i khi chÃºng ta gá»i káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng diá»…n ra lÃ  hiá»‡n thá»±c vÃ  káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng khÃ´ng diá»…n ra lÃ  giáº£ tÆ°á»Ÿng.</p>

<p>ChÃºng ta dÃ¹ng chá»‰ sá»‘ dÆ°á»›i Ä‘á»ƒ kÃ­ hiá»‡u:</p>

<p>\(Y_{0i}\) lÃ  káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng  cá»§a cÃ¡ thá»ƒ i khÃ´ng Ä‘Æ°á»£c can thiá»‡p (Ä‘á»‘i chá»©ng).</p>

<p>\(Y_{1i}\) lÃ  káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng  cá»§a cÃ¡ thá»ƒ i Ä‘Æ°á»£c can thiá»‡p.</p>

<p>LÆ°u Ã½ Ä‘Ã´i khi chÃºng ta nhÃ¬n tháº¥y cÃ¡c káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng Ä‘Æ°á»£c kÃ­ hiá»‡u dÆ°á»›i dáº¡ng hÃ m sá»‘ \(Y_i(t)\). \(Y_{0i}\) cÃ³ thá»ƒ lÃ  \(Y_i(0)\) vÃ  \(Y_{1i}\) cÃ³ thá»ƒ lÃ  \(Y_i(1)\). á» Ä‘Ã¢y chÃºng ta sáº½ chá»§ yáº¿u dÃ¹ng chá»‰ sá»‘ dÆ°á»›i Ä‘á»ƒ kÃ­ hiá»‡u.</p>

<p><img src="./data/img/intro/potential_outcomes.png" alt="img" /></p>

<p>Trong vÃ­ dá»¥ mÃ¡y tÃ­nh báº£ng cá»§a chÃºng ta, \(Y_{1i}\) lÃ  káº¿t quáº£ há»c táº­p cá»§a há»c sinh i náº¿u Ä‘Æ°á»£c phÃ¡t mÃ¡y tÃ­nh báº£ng dÃ¹ng trong lá»›p há»c.  BÃ¢y giá», náº¿u há»c sinh i Ä‘Æ°á»£c phÃ¡t mÃ¡y tÃ­nh báº£ng, chÃºng ta quan sÃ¡t tháº¥y \(Y_{1i}\). Náº¿u khÃ´ng, \(Y_{1i}\) váº«n tá»“n táº¡i trÃªn lÃ­ thuyáº¿t nhÆ°ng chÃºng ta khÃ´ng thá»ƒ quan sÃ¡t. Trong trÆ°á»ng há»£p nÃ y nÃ³ lÃ  má»™t káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng (giáº£ tÆ°á»Ÿng).</p>

<p>Vá»›i káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng, chÃºng ta cÃ³ thá»ƒ Ä‘á»‹nh nghÄ©a hiá»‡u á»©ng can thiá»‡p cÃ¡ thá»ƒ:</p>

<p>\(Y_{1i} - Y_{0i}\)</p>

<p>Táº¥t nhiÃªn, do thÃ¡ch thá»©c cÆ¡ báº£n cá»§a suy luáº­n nhÃ¢n quáº£, chÃºng ta khÃ´ng bao giá» biáº¿t Ä‘Æ°á»£c hiá»‡u á»©ng can thiá»‡p cÃ¡ thá»ƒ vÃ¬ chÃºng ta chá»‰ cÃ³ thá»ƒ quan sÃ¡t Ä‘Æ°á»£c 1 trong 2 káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng. VÃ¬ váº­y, hÃ£y táº­p trung Æ°á»›c lÆ°á»£ng má»™t Ä‘áº¡i lÆ°á»£ng Ä‘Æ¡n giáº£n hÆ¡n: <strong>tÃ¡c Ä‘á»™ng can thiá»‡p trung bÃ¬nh (Average Treatment Effect - ATE)</strong>. Äáº¡i lÆ°á»£ng nÃ y Ä‘Æ°á»£c Ä‘á»‹nh nghÄ©a nhÆ° sau:</p>

<p>\(ATE = E[Y_1 - Y_0]\)</p>

<p>Trong Ä‘Ã³ E[â€¦] lÃ  giÃ¡ trá»‹ kÃ¬ vá»ng. Má»™t Ä‘áº¡i lÆ°á»£ng dá»… Æ°á»›c tÃ­nh hÆ¡n ná»¯a lÃ  <strong>tÃ¡c Ä‘á»™ng can thiá»‡p trung bÃ¬nh trÃªn nhÃ³m Ä‘Æ°Æ¡c can thiá»‡p (Average Treatment Effect on the Treated- ATET)</strong>:</p>

<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>\(ATET = E[Y_1 - Y_0</td>
      <td>T=1]\)</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>ChÃºng ta biáº¿t ráº±ng sáº½ khÃ´ng bao giá» cÃ³ thá»ƒ quan sÃ¡t Ä‘Æ°á»£c cáº£ 2 káº¿t quáº£ tiá»m nÄƒng, nhÆ°ng Ä‘á»ƒ dá»… hiá»ƒu hÆ¡n, hÃ£y táº¡m giáº£ thiáº¿t lÃ  ta cÃ³ thá»ƒ. Giáº£ sá»­ chÃºng ta thu tháº­p dá»¯ liá»‡u cho 4 trÆ°á»ng há»c. ChÃºng ta quan sÃ¡t Ä‘Æ°á»£c tá»«ng trÆ°á»ng cÃ³ phÃ¡t mÃ¡y tÃ­nh báº£ng cho há»c sinh hay khÃ´ng vÃ  káº¿t quáº£ há»c táº­p cá»§a há»c sinh. á» Ä‘Ã¢y viá»‡c phÃ¡t mÃ¡y tÃ­nh báº£ng lÃ  can thiá»‡p, vÃ¬ tháº¿ \(T=1\) tÆ°Æ¡ng á»©ng vá»›i viá»‡c phÃ¡t mÃ¡y tÃ­nh báº£ng cho há»c sinh. \(Y\) lÃ  Ä‘iá»ƒm sá»‘.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">pd</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">dict</span><span class="p">(</span>
    <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">],</span>
